2019-11-17 22-00-00:
	Title: Release 20191117
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: Just in time for the holiday season, release-20191117 is now available with all of the features and fixes that have been tested and refined over the past few months:\n\n  • Save/Load support for missions and skirmish\n  • A new spectator/replay interface\n  • A new in-game UI for Tiberian Dawn\n  • Improved order queuing behavior\n  • Direction selection for aircraft-based support powers\n  • Fixed several issues with left-click mouse controls\n  • Balance changes for RA and TD\n  • Fixes for many bugs and graphical glitches\n\nSee the full news post at www.openra.net for a video overview and the release download!
